Description: Indicates the segment type, always 'DS03' for this payload.
The length of the segment, which is fixed at 139 bytes.
Indicates if the file is less than 36 months or matching logic is false (M in this case).
Indicates a match found in directory services (Y in this case).
Indicates if a hit was found in the credit bureau (N means no hit).
Indicates whether the last name matched (N for no match).
Indicates whether the first name matched (N for no match).
Indicates whether the middle name matched (N for no match).
Indicates whether the street or civic number matched (N for no match).
Indicates whether the street name matched (M for partial match).
Indicates whether the apartment number matched (N for no match).
Indicates whether the city name matched (N for no match).
Indicates whether the province matched (N for no match).
Indicates whether the postal code matched (N for no match).
Indicates whether the telephone number matched (M for partial match).
Indicates whether the date of birth matched (N for no match).
Indicates whether the SIN (Social Insurance Number) matched (H for partial match on the last 4 digits).
Indicates if fraud was detected (H for high fraud risk).
The person's last name, padded to fit a length of 20 characters.
The person's first name, padded to fit a length of 16 characters.
The person's middle name, padded to fit a length of 10 characters.
The street or civic number of the person's address, padded to fit a length of 8 characters.
The street name of the person's address, padded to fit a length of 24 characters.
The city name of the person's address, padded to fit a length of 16 characters.
The province code for the person's address, 2 characters long.
The postal code for the person's address, 6 characters long.
